        <message_html><![CDATA[<p>Dear ${user_information.first_name}&nbsp; ${user_information.last_name},</p>
<p>Thank you for your loan application with LoanShark. We&rsquo;re pleased to inform you that your application has successfully <span style="color: rgb(22, 145, 121);"><strong>PASSED</strong></span> the <strong><span style="color: rgb(22, 145, 121);">LOAN OFFICER APPROVAL</span>.</strong></p>
<h3>What's Next?</h3>
<p>Your application is now being reviewed by one of our <strong>FINANCIAL OFFICERS</strong> for the third step of approval. This process involves a more in-depth evaluation, and our team will contact you if any additional information or documentation is needed.</p>
<h3>Application Summary</h3>
<ul style="list-style-position: inside;">
<li>Application ID: ${number}</li>
<li>Loan Amount: ${loan_amount}</li>
<li>Application Date: ${sys_created_on}</li>
</ul>
<p>You can track the status of your loan application anytime by logging into your account on our website or contacting our customer service team.</p>
<p>We appreciate your patience during this process and look forward to assisting you with your financial needs.</p>
<p>Best regards,</p>
<p>LoanSharks</p>]]></message_html>
